I"	<h1 id="php-강조-표시--s">PHP 강조 표시 -s</h1>
<p>-s 옵션은 PHP 소스의 문법을 강조하여 HTML 파일 형태로 출력합니다.</p>

<p>예제 파일 index.php</p>
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="cp">&lt;?php</span>
<span class="k">echo</span> <span class="s2">"PHP LocalServer Test"</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="nb">phpinfo</span><span class="p">();</span>
<span class="cp">?&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>C:\php-7.1.4-Win32-VC14-x86&gt;php -s index.php
&lt;code&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #007700"&gt;echo&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #DD0000"&gt;"PHP&amp;nbsp;LocalServer&amp;nbsp;Test"&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #0000BB"&gt;?&amp;gt;fo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #007700"&gt;();
&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

